" Ruby Tab Configuration
setlocal tabstop=2 " Display <Tab> as two spaces in visual mode.
setlocal softtabstop=2 " Insert <Tab> as two spaces when editing.
setlocal shiftwidth=2 " Insert <Tab> as two spaces when auto-indenting.
setlocal expandtab " In insert mode, use the appropriate number of spaes for <Tab>.

" Set listchars for tabs and trailing spaces.
setlocal listchars=tab:>-,trail:- 
setlocal list
